{"tid":2316144,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[模擬飛行JJ]Digital Combat Simulator World","createTime":"2020-12-07T15:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T13:52:08.000Z","uid":34300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"94a7ea66536a17f7a4ab73bc2122f9a198a8283b","tid":2316144,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T15:51:58.000Z","msg":"大家War Thunder 就聽得多<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔知大家有無興趣玩一隻更加真實既模擬戰機飛行既遊戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n數位戰鬥模擬世界（英語：Digital Combat Simulator World，簡稱DCS World）是由Eagle Dynamics開發，The Fighter Collection發行的一款空戰模擬遊戲。 大家有興趣既話可以上DCS World 官網睇下 <a href=\"https://www.digitalcombatsimulator.com/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.digitalcombatsimulator.com%2Fen%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=7fe1ab5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.digitalcombatsimulator.com/en/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依隻遊戲是用DLC 制，每當你購買一隻戰機之後，就可以終身享受，其中包括大家熟悉既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nF16C Viper<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1090850/ss_9344732ab21f59e102e48b0b649bd892a77631f7.1920x1080.jpg?t=1596105274\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1090850%2Fss_9344732ab21f59e102e48b0b649bd892a77631f7.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1596105274&h=c6a4b41e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1090850/ss_5f1fb7d592a016140f2ed6c6a50dea7587c2bb89.600x338.jpg?t=1596105274\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1090850%2Fss_5f1fb7d592a016140f2ed6c6a50dea7587c2bb89.600x338.jpg%3Ft%3D1596105274&h=9f7e895e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nF-14A/B Tomcat<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/411893/ss_f1acb9e353befd446c3c7e69c68d0e0485757e11.1920x1080.jpg?t=1606514762\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F411893%2Fss_f1acb9e353befd446c3c7e69c68d0e0485757e11.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1606514762&h=e4a13e8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/411893/ss_1488e8087419b46f3b92edda9c0ff2696a81249a.1920x1080.jpg?t=1606514762\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F411893%2Fss_1488e8087419b46f3b92edda9c0ff2696a81249a.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1606514762&h=325d3ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nF/A-18C Hornet<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/411950/ss_150ac236350e29fbd9b8e1dc83a71031aae9d80a.1920x1080.jpg?t=1601479936\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F411950%2Fss_150ac236350e29fbd9b8e1dc83a71031aae9d80a.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1601479936&h=92ecca91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/411950/ss_b6c3de26d872a58f505f97271027293ea88e8a19.1920x1080.jpg?t=1601479936\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F411950%2Fss_b6c3de26d872a58f505f97271027293ea88e8a19.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1601479936&h=8ffd2ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買咗艦載機，仲可以係遊戲裡面既航母升降添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1120305/ss_6edaf8761124b19a2981fd83ebecc1e75c6b8cb5.1920x1080.jpg?t=1591404258\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1120305%2Fss_6edaf8761124b19a2981fd83ebecc1e75c6b8cb5.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1591404258&h=b1f8e634&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/1120305/ss_8160dbfe4c893398588390d31b2197b5b674bbe8.1920x1080.jpg?t=1591404258\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.cloudflare.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F1120305%2Fss_8160dbfe4c893398588390d31b2197b5b674bbe8.1920x1080.jpg%3Ft%3D1591404258&h=c5b84b81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰機，機炮，狗鬥，簡直係男人既浪漫，依D都係fight simulator 比唔到你既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於DCS 同真實既戰機無乜大分別，所以入手時需要有人指導，只要你加入我們Navyc，就會得到老機司指導<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n我們既Discord係<a href=\"https://discord.gg/3WKv4ssp5C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F3WKv4ssp5C&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7PG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=5257e8ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/3WKv4ssp5C</a>"},{"pid":"e707da1fc9e304e47d7d8e0214a28041435abdfa","tid":2316144,"uid":34300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T00:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d339ca88c3c69ee54c031672caaf72aa096bec85